Sometimes you just have to scratch your head!
John 10:40 in the NIV version says, &ldquo;Then Jesus went back across the Jordan to the place where John had been baptizing in the early days. There he stayed.&rdquo;
When Samuel read aloud the Waran version of that verse and one of the checkers gave a translation into the Tok Pisin language, the consultant thought he heard something odd. He asked the checkers, &ldquo;Who was baptizing?
